title: Windy Corner Market and Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Southern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Atmosphere of a country market. Menu is meat stuff but has a tofu po-boy sandwich with barbecue sauce; a nut and tofu burger; a few veg salads including a super food salad with greens, sprouts, pumpkin seeds, chickpeas, and house-made crispy tofu; steamed veggie bowl with brown rice and crispy tofu. Sells gluten-free cake mixes, preserves, grits, seeds, and other foodstuff. Has Wi-Fi.
